somewhat slowly. 1971, I formed Peter Paul

03:25.897 --> 03:32.683
Petroleum Company that still exists today. 
Principal partner in Peter Paul Petroleum

03:34.305 --> 03:40.130
Company is Princeton University Endowment Fund. 
