03:41.178 --> 03:45.802
million worth of oil and gas properties. So we're 
very active. Good. You're very active in small

03:48.645 --> 03:50.207
fields? Mostly small fields. We do not 
participate in offshore. We don't do deep

03:54.311 --> 03:55.812
drilling. But we do drill a good many wells. But 
